      "created_at": "2022-11-05T08:05:54.084Z",
      "cooked": "<p>natën</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/9/e/9e3ba32f5d536aed72058d4b56bba51101576121.jpeg\" alt=\"immagine\" data-base62-sha1=\"mzNdcCkYnx40No2mqJA7988Xx97\" width=\"300\" height=\"380\"></p>",
