      "created_at": "2022-12-08T02:16:01.742Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Manjola, pashe ne email qe me kishe derguar edhe ti nje kartoline. Do me falesh. Te kujtova Sanco Pance po ti na qenke Dylqinje. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
